### Get all items
GET {{Hostname}}/items HTTP/1.1

### Get item by id
# @prompt Id
GET {{Hostname}}/items/{{Id}} HTTP/1.1

### DELETE item by id
# @prompt Id
DELETE {{Hostname}}/items/{{Id}} HTTP/1.1

